concept.title: SNMP Trap OIDs

othermeta.name: shortdesc
othermeta.content: Catalog of SNMP trap OIDs sent by the network management card and instructions for configuring trap destinations and handling alarms.

othermeta.name: entities
othermeta.content: snmp traps; trap oids; network management card AP9635; mib entries; trap destinations; monitoring system

div.p: Any active traps can be view from a management information base (MIB) browser with correctly configured trap receiver connected to the NMC.
The following table shows the different traps that can be sent out from the NMC when triggered. The NMC will only send out the traps that are currently triggered in the system.
div.note: Base OID Address for APC / Reality: 1.3.6.1.4.1.318.
